				</div>
				<div class="one-half column detail-content">
					<h3>Advanced Frequency Scanning</h3>
					<p>Our patented technology scans over 9,000 frequencies in your body to identify areas of imbalance, stress, and dysfunction. Within minutes, you'll have a complete picture of your body's energetic state.</p>
					
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Check"> Scans nervous system frequencies</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Check"> Identifies stress patterns</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Check"> Detects energy blockages</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Check"> Maps organ system health</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="row detail-row reverse">
				<div class="one-half column detail-content">
					<h3>Targeted Healing Vibrations</h3>
					<p>Once your scan is complete, the Alpha AH device delivers specific healing frequencies directly to the areas that need support. These gentle vibrations help your body remember its natural state of balance.</p>
					
					<ul class="feature-list">
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Energy"> Restores cellular energy</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Energy"> Reduces inflammation</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Energy"> Improves circulation</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Energy"> Enhances recovery</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="one-half column">
					<img src={ProductShowcase2.src} alt="Healing Process" class="detail-image">
