						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Portable"> Very lightweight, only 300 Grams</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Portable"> Ultra-portable design</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Portable"> Rechargeable battery life up to 6 hours</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Portable"> Silent operation</li>
						<li><img src={Check.src} alt="Portable"> Works with smartphone app</li>
