					</p>
					<div class="feature-highlights">
						<li>Comprehensive health monitoring</li>
						<li>Seamless app integration</li>
						<li>Real-time vital metrics</li>
						<li>Personalized insights</li>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-image science-backed">
						<div class="feature-icon-large glow">​🚀​</div>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-title">Science-Backed and Innovative</div>
					<p class="feature-description">
						Built on cutting-edge research and technology, the Alpha Wearable provides a modern, reliable approach to achieving optimal wellness.
					</p>
					<div class="feature-highlights">
						<li>Advanced bioresonance technology</li>
						<li>Clinically validated methods</li>
						<li>Innovative frequency therapy</li>
						<li>Research-based solutions</li>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card device-showcase">
