						</p>
						<div class="feature-highlights">
							<li>Medical-grade materials</li>
							<li>Ergonomic comfort design</li>
							<li>Wireless connectivity</li>
							<li>Compatible with Android and iOS</li>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="wellness-showcase">
				<div class="showcase-content">
					<div class="showcase-left">
						<h2 class="showcase-title">Revolutionary Wellness Technology</h2>
						<div class="showcase-features">
							<div class="showcase-feature">
								<div class="feature-icon-mini">🔬</div>
								<div class="feature-text">
									<h4>Bio-Scan Technology</h4>
									<p>Advanced Technology with in-depth wellness reports. Monitors Heart Rate, Blood Pressure, and Blood Oxygen</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="showcase-feature">
								<div class="feature-icon-mini">📱</div>
								<div class="feature-text">
									<h4>Smart App Integration</h4>
									<p>Seamless connectivity with real-time monitoring of vital metrics and sleep patterns</p>
								</div>
							</div>
