			<p class="section-subtitle">Thousands of users report significant improvements in these key areas:</p>
			
			<div class="benefits-grid">
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">😴</div>
					<h3>Better Sleep</h3>
					<p>Fall asleep faster, sleep deeper, and wake up refreshed. Users report 73% improvement in sleep quality within the first week.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">🏃</div>
					<h3>More Energy</h3>
					<p>Natural, sustained energy without caffeine or stimulants. Feel vibrant and alert throughout your day.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">🤍</div>
					<h3>Pain Relief</h3>
					<p>Reduce chronic pain, muscle tension, and inflammation naturally. Many users experience relief within hours.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">💭​</div>
					<h3>Mental Clarity</h3>
					<p>Clear brain fog, improve focus, and enhance cognitive function. Think sharper and feel more present.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">🙂​</div>
					<h3>Stress Relief</h3>
					<p>Calm your nervous system and reduce anxiety naturally. Feel more balanced and resilient to daily stressors.</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="benefit-card">
					<div class="feature-icon-mini2">​🧘​</div>
					<h3>Overall Wellness</h3>
					<p>Support your body's natural healing processes for improved digestion, immunity, and vitality.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- How It Works Section -->
	<section class="how-it-works">
		<div class="container">
			<h2>How It Works - Simple as 1, 2, 3</h2>
			
			<div class="steps-container">
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-number">1</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Turn on the Device and Download the App</h3>
						<p>Install the Anywhere Healing app from the App Store or Google Play Store. Place the device on your body and run a comprehensive frequency scan. The device reads your body's natural frequencies and identifies areas of imbalance. </p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-number">2</div>
					<div class="step-content">
