						<p>Pair the Alpha Wearable with the app via Bluetooth for seamless communication. Activate the therapy feature through the app to begin the healing process. Based on your scan results, the device will restore balance and promote healing.</p>

					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-number">3</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Feel the Difference</h3>
						<p>Experience immediate and lasting improvements in energy, sleep, pain relief, and overall well-being. Use daily for optimal results. Feel the therapeutic frequencies restore balance and promote well-being in your body.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Scientific Backing Section -->
